# IP-sensitive content — never for public repo.
# suspended/: DOS game files extracted from E's legally-owned "Lost Treasures of
# Infocom" copy, used only as a personal reference for hand-authoring an original
# DAVE module. Not open-license source (see historicalsource/suspended README).
# modules/suspended_demo/: original content inspired by the reference above, for
# personal use and demonstration only — not for distribution. If a distributable
# Suspended import feature is ever built (see docs/future_features.md §7), it will
# be a separate user-verified import utility, not this seed data.
suspended/
modules/suspended_demo/

# Reference material (local copies for module development; not for publication)
# Published modules include a references.md in the module directory listing sources with URLs.
references/

